llvm 169461
clang 169462


>>>BUG1207a:
<example>
    for (int i=....) {
        a[i] = ... ;  // a is a member

    }

    GEP of a[i] is dependent on i, which has a local scope smaller than function scope.
    when inserting GEP before return, i is not defined!!!
<solution>

>>>ADD sh wrapper

>>>firefox
(1) .mozconfig: set
    CC=clang
    CXX=clang++

(2) make -f config.mk configure
(3) cd /obj-dir****
(4) ./config/autoconf.mk
    ./js/src/config/autoconf.mk

change CXX and HOST_CXX =/home/jing/src/APIRace/bin/clang-apirace.sh

(5) /obj-dir***/memory/mozalloc/Makefile 

add CXX and HOST_CXX = clang++

(6) make -j 10


